"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641294823,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"U-V0KbZo5zukYQ5stLJM6RzZ6ZLaTmsqVrW5-1oCSNc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x76ad8583dafB7d6058Ae895a637caD1d5d670619\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"mVpGejG-dMVzKZaWjigrGpf1C7huzVAFQEhFqGf6tyY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"C2-vz0pJ_mVqT_A4gIwkDmAC5TVZvVRoQREK4VGhES0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"-WlbvswPb-2KwyNpOEzHfJ28FfWq2QLC7nQtSuKAKPdX1FYXFzI3fXXVsMYBh6lt_LGq-7Zn0LjzvrQ7wymh6A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x937072b8905b78fd42f51d707267060ee450368c88379aeede7fb5906daa5d3d4a8a9e1e79a9328280c3d9bb3f9d34214ce483a363713be536e463171084ea781c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"mVpGejG-dMVzKZaWjigrGpf1C7huzVAFQEhFqGf6tyY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"C2-vz0pJ_mVqT_A4gIwkDmAC5TVZvVRoQREK4VGhES0\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi